    {
        "content": "<p>kind of an off topic comment but I really liked this book - <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Everything-More-Compact-History-Infinity/dp/0393339289\">https://www.amazon.com/Everything-More-Compact-History-Infinity/dp/0393339289</a> - about the history of mathematicians trying to figure out whether infinity was a legitimate number or not and how to deal with it or even think about it. once I saw how these smart people in the past were confused by it, i had more sympathy for modern people that find it unintuitive</p>",
        "id": 216254092,
